items.title: Awesome Tdengine Updates on Apr 25 - May 01, 2022
items.summary: 35 awesome projects updated on Apr 25 - May 01, 2022
items.content_text:
### GUI

*   [Taos.Studio (‚≠ê87)](https://github.com/maikebing/Taos.Studio) - A GUI tool for viewing and editing data for TDengine.
*   [balloonfish (‚≠ê9)](https://github.com/xielaoshi99/balloonfish) - Electron + Vue3 + Vite2.0 based TDengine time-series database visualized management tool.
*   [tdengine-client (‚≠ê3)](https://github.com/wurong1420/tdengine-client) - A simple TDengine interface.

### IoT

*   [DG-IoT (‚≠ê273)](https://github.com/dgiot/dgiot-dashboard) - DG-IoT platform industry application extension plugin.
*   [dgiot\_tdengine (‚≠ê1)](https://github.com/dgiot/dgiot_tdengine) - TDengine adapter plugin.
*   [node-red-contrib-tdengine (‚≠ê11)](https://github.com/kp45-tech/node-red-contrib-tdengine) - TDengine connector plugin for Node-RED.

### ORM

*   [sqli (‚≠ê1.9k)](https://github.com/x-ream/sqli) - ORM SQL Interface, Criteria, CriteriaBuilder, ResultMapBuilder.
*   [TDengine ORM Framework (‚≠ê6)](https://github.com/hxshun/TDengineORM) - ORM framework of TAOS Data's time-series database TDengine.
*   [IoTSharp.EntityFrameworkCore.Taos (‚≠ê171)](https://github.com/IoTSharp/EntityFrameworkCore.Taos) - Entity, Framework, EF, Core, Data, O/RM, entity-framework-core, TDengine.
*   [tdengine-orm (‚≠ê13)](https://github.com/Yurunsoft/tdengine-orm) - TDengine ORM based on tdengine-restful-connector & php-tdengine.<!--lint ignore awesome-list-item-->
*   [crown (‚≠ê36)](https://github.com/machine-w/crown) - crown is a simple and small ORM for TDengine.

### Connector

*   [PDO\_TAOS (‚≠ê40)](https://github.com/bearlord/pdo_taos) - TDengine driver for PDO.
*   [yii2-tdengine (‚≠ê0)](https://github.com/bearlord/yii2-tdengine) - TDengine for yii2, pdo\_taos needed.
*   [php-tdengine (‚≠ê76)](https://github.com/Yurunsoft/php-tdengine) - PHP extension of TDengine, supports Swoole.
*   [tdengine-restful-connector (‚≠ê18)](https://github.com/Yurunsoft/tdengine-restful-connector) - PHP extension of TDengine, support Swoole.
*   [imi-tdengine (‚≠ê5)](https://github.com/imiphp/imi-tdengine) - Encapsulated TDengine connection pools, used in imi framework.
*   [pytaos (‚≠ê1)](https://github.com/horennel/pytaos) - Python RESTful API of TDengine.
*   [NestJS TDengine Driver (‚≠ê2)](https://github.com/IricBing/nestjs-tdengine) - NestJS TDengine Driver(RESTful based).
*   [taos-rs](https://github.com/yuerrd/taos-rs) - TDengine Java RESTful Client.
*   [TDengine Rust bindings (‚≠ê7)](https://github.com/songtianyi/tdengine-rust-bindings) - It's a Rust bindings project for TDengine.
*   [TDenginex](https://github.com/lizhaochao/TDenginex) - TDengine Connector for Elixir.

### Stack

*   [NewLife.Core (‚≠ê1.8k)](https://github.com/NewLifeX/X) - NewLife.Core Database core.
*   [NewLife.XCode (‚≠ê87)](https://github.com/NewLifeX/NewLife.XCode) - NewLife.XCode Database Middle-ware.

### Plugin

*   [rsyslog plugin for tdengine (‚≠ê2)](https://github.com/mxmkeep/rsyslog-omtaos) - rsyslog plugin for TDengine.
*   [HiveMQ TDengine Plugin (‚≠ê7)](https://github.com/huskar-t/hivemq-tdengine-extension) - HiveMQ TDengine Plugin.
*   [hivemq-tdengine-jdsl-extension (‚≠ê0)](https://github.com/huskar-t/hivemq-tdengine-jdsl-extension) - HiveMQ TDengine JDSL Plugin.
*   [HiveMQ-TDengine-Extension (‚≠ê1)](https://github.com/john-bigz/hivemq-tdengine-extension) - A TDengine extension for HiveMQ.

### Data

*   [tsarchive (‚≠ê3)](https://github.com/cenc-cea/tsarchive) - Consume data streams from a Kafka topic, archive the data packets into the TDengine time series database.
*   [YoMo x TDengine (‚≠ê2)](https://github.com/fanweixiao/push-stream-logging) - Streaming high frequency logs to TDengine.<!--lint ignore awesome-list-item-->

### Container

*   [TDengine cluster for kubernetes (‚≠ê16)](https://github.com/wwbgo/tdengine-k8s) - TDengine cluster for kubernetes.

### Distribution

*   [tdengine-client-macos-unofficial (‚≠ê0)](https://github.com/cybartists/tdengine-client-macos-unofficial) - Unofficial compiled TDengine client for macOS.
*   [Unofficial TDengine Windows](https://github.com/GitHubForzhenjiazhao/Soft) - Unofficial TDengine Windows client & server package.

### Others

*   [auto\_taos\_cfg (‚≠ê0)](https://github.com/glzhao89/auto_taos_cfg) - Auto generate TDengine log/data/cfg.
*   [Sentinel Console (‚≠ê1)](https://github.com/wenhao/sentinel-dashboard-tdengine) - Sentinel-Dashboard with TDengine.
*   [Davinci (‚≠ê5k)](https://github.com/edp963/davinci) - Davinci is a DVsaaS (Data Visualization as a Service) Platform.

items.content_text:
### IoT

*   [Zeus IoT (‚≠ê706)](https://github.com/zmops/zeus-iot) - Zeus IoT is the world's first open source Internet of Things distributed collection platform based on Zabbix, with the ability to collect, analyze, and store data from millions of IoT devices.

### Connector

### Plugin

*   [Integrate TDengine to YoMo](https://github.com/yomorun/yomo-sink-tdengine-example) - Demonstrates how to integrate TDengine to YoMo and store data to TDengine after stream processing.
*   [taostd (‚≠ê1)](https://github.com/nzhzds/taostd) - taostd is a simple sql executor for TDengine.

### Algorithm

*   [PyODDS (‚≠ê254)](https://github.com/datamllab/pyodds) - An End-to-end Outlier Detection System.
*   [PYTSDA-TDengine (‚≠ê22)](https://github.com/Shawshank-Smile/PYTSDA-TDengine) - An End-to-end time series data analysis system with TDengine.

### Observability

### Container

*   [TDengine Containers (‚≠ê3)](https://github.com/arktos-venture/docker-tdengine) - TDengine Client, Node, Adapter and Arbitrator Rootless and smallest containers as possible.
*   [TDengine-K8S (‚≠ê0)](https://github.com/elihe2011/TDengine-K8S)

### Dataset

*   [seedlink2taos\_py (‚≠ê11)](https://github.com/schenton/seedlink2taos_py) - A Python program that fetches seismic waveform data from IRIS and writes to TDengine database.
